author: Matt Ellentuck
title: Florida Gulf Coast player dunked so hard he broke the shot clock
text:
DUNK CITY IS BACK!
Florida Gulf Coast’s Rayjon Tucker dunked a basketball so hard that he broke the shot clock.
Rayjon Tucker pic.twitter.com/IhZOqemhtQ 
— Abdul Memon (@abdulamemon) March 5, 2017 Oh my, the shot clock literally shut off. It couldn’t bare to spend another second as a functional piece of equipment because it just witnessed madness. The shot clock has to take some time to really think about what just happened.
The Eagles are playing the North Florida Ospreys in the Atlantic Sun final, and the winner gets an automatic bid to the NCAA Tournament.
Dunk City is back!
